import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Table ,Button,Checkbox} from 'semantic-ui-react' export default class showRows extends Component{ constructor(props) { super(props); } render() { const info=this.props.info return ( { this.props.info.map((e,index)=>( {index} {e.info[0]} {e.info[1]} {e.info[2]} {e.info[3]} {e.info[4]}/{info[5]} {info[6]} )) }
) } }
